        "timestamp": "2020-03-04 18:17:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n> \n> (1 comment)\n> \n> minor typo to be corrected.. btw, does this require any change to blueprints imports (e.g holmes)?\n\nNo.  Holmes is using the type file with the version 1.1.0.  There is no other type file available.  The 1.1.0 type file is referencing pgaas plugin version 1.2.0.  This change has the bootstrap container load the 1.2.0 pgaas plugin (and the 1.1.0 sshkeyshare plugin) so that the plugins referenced by the type files will be available.  \n\nThis has been tested.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
